OL,3,CThe Box wins national museum award
OL,5,FThe Box in Plymouth has won a national
OL,6,Fmuseum award for its "ambitious and
OL,7,Fwelcoming approach".
OL,9,FThe attraction has been recognised as
OL,10,Fthe Art Fund Museum of the Year 2026.
OL,11,FVictoria Pomery OBE, Chief Executive
OL,12,Fof The Box, accepted the #120,000
OL,13,Fprize at a ceremony on board the Cutty
OL,14,FSark.
OL,16,FThe Box tells the story of Plymouth
OL,17,Fthrough more than 2 million artworks,
OL,18,Fobjects, specimens, and archival
OL,19,Fmaterials. It's welcomed more than 1.3
OL,20,Fmillion visitors since opening in 2020.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
