OL,3,CThe Box wins national museum award
OL,5,FJudges say the attraction brings
OL,6,Ftogether extraordinary collections,
OL,7,Fexhibitions and archives under one
OL,8,Froof, alongside impactful community
OL,9,Fwork and a deep commitment to access
OL,10,Ffor all.
OL,12,FJenny Waldman, Director of Art Fund
OL,13,Fand chair of the judges for Art Fund
OL,14,FMuseum of the Year, described The Box
OL,15,Fas "A revelation in so many ways - a
OL,16,Ftrue jewel in the crown of the South
OL,17,FWest".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
