OL,3,CThe Box wins national museum award
OL,5,F"In just five years, it has
OL,6,Ftransformed how Plymouth's remarkable
OL,7,Fcollections are shared and
OL,8,Fexperienced, creating a welcoming
OL,9,Fspace for visitors and reaching beyond
OL,10,Fits walls into public spaces and
OL,11,Falmost every school in the city.
OL,13,F"Its social and economic impact
OL,14,Fdemonstrates what long-term investment
OL,15,Fin culture can achieve ` and is
OL,16,Frecognised and championed by Plymouth
OL,17,FCity Council."
OL,19,FJune Sarpong OBE, broadcaster and
OL,20,Fjudge for Art Fund Museum of the Year
OL,21,F2026, said:
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
