OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782839909
OL,3,CThe Box wins national museum award
OL,5,F"What stood out so strongly with The
OL,6,FBox was the sense of pride and
OL,7,Fconnection it has created across
OL,8,FPlymouth. From local groups such as
OL,9,Fthe Windrush community to its
OL,10,Fpartnerships with the university, it
OL,11,Fis a museum that genuinely belongs to
OL,12,Fthe people it serves.
OL,14,F"Through exhibitions that uncover
OL,15,Foverlooked histories to welcoming
OL,16,Fspaces for learning and creativity,
OL,17,FThe Box is reimagining what being a
OL,18,Fmuseum can mean."
